	Stewart Capital Advisors, LLC



































Stewart Capital Advisors, LLC is an SEC registered advisory firm specializing in the management of value-styled portfolios. We focus on research and valuation using a bottom-up approach with a focus on the long term.
We offer separate account management for public funds, corporations, endowments, foundations, and other sub-advised accounts. Our investment strategies are available to institutional investors and to individuals through their financial intermediaries.



