	WHEREAS

	, UMBFS, UMBDS, and the Trust desire to amend the Administration and Accounting Agreement, the Transfer Agency Agreement, the Distribution Agreement, and the Inbound Call Management and Fulfillment Services Agreement (each referred to as an “Agreement” and collectively referred to as the “Agreements”) as applicable in accordance with terms thereof;






